reviewText: Buy this now if you adore H-Anime Maids!!!

This is not a story per se, more a collection of scenes from other hentais... which sounds like s*** but honestly, I could have saved a few bucks getting just this. Only real downside, imo, is this only has the s***ty English voice option and no subtitles. Otherwise a good deal.

This was not the movie that I though it was. It was nothing more than a series of scenes involving maids. I personally detest and abhore the bondage, brutalization and demeaning acts portrayed in this film. There is an anime about maids where the male has five or six that take care of him after something happened and it was both funny and had decent  sex scenes that both the wife and I could watch together. This one will go into the dumpster. Perhaps some demented individuals may enjoy the rape and insertions of various objects, but I don't.
